{"type":"message","id":"95351367","parentId":"3c011ec4","timestamp":"2026-03-24T07:47:46.426Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_l50daxfrhpi6_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 4906\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=1086\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] the\r\n[mutation proposed] the\r\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 034714 - The COMPRESSION-CAUSAL DUALITY insight is documented but the TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment hasn't been implemented yet. I need to create the actual classifier to test the hypothesis that causal structure IS invariant structure.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"salty-cedar","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 4906\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=1086\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] the\r\n[mutation proposed] the\r\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 034714 - The COMPRESSION-CAUSAL DUALITY insight is documented but the TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment hasn't been implemented yet. I need to create the actual classifier to test the hypothesis that causal structure IS invariant structure.\r\n","name":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pulse.ps1"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774338466424}}
{"type":"message","id":"05108cce","parentId":"95351367","timestamp":"2026-03-24T07:47:46.428Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_l50daxfrhpi6_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"﻿# Pulse: 2026-03-24 034616\n\n## Applied Mutations\nNo mutations applied this cycle.\nRejected: src/tic_classifier.py (missing)\n\n## LLM Response\n<think>\r\nLet me analyze the current state and determine the best single action to advance the goals.\r\n\r\nLooking at the pending actions and the Phase 1 Advancement note:\r\n- The next action is to implement the TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment\r\n- This involves implementing a TIC classifier on `logs/pulse_*.md` files\r\n- Measuring invariant/variant classification accuracy\r\n- Predicting next pulse content from invariants\r\n- Validating against success criteria (>70%, >60%)\r\n\r\nThis is the most concrete next step. Let me create a TIC experiment implementation that:\r\n1. Reads the last N pulse logs\r\n2. Identifies invariant vs variant elements across pulses\r\n3. Attempts to predict next pulse content\r\n4. Reports accuracy metrics\r\n\r\nI should create a new file `research/tic_experiment.ps1` or similar that implements this.\r\n</think>\r\n\r\n### OBSERVATION\r\nThe TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment is the next critical step to validate the COMPRESSION-CAUSAL DUALITY hypothesis. I need to implement a classifier that identifies invariant vs variant patterns across pulse logs and tests prediction accuracy.\r\n\r\n### ACTION\r\nCreate a PowerShell implementation of the TIC classifier that:\r\n1. Extracts patterns from recent pulse logs\r\n2. Classifies content as invariant (causal) vs variant\r\n3. Tests next-pulse prediction accuracy\r\n4. Reports metrics against success criteria\r\n\r\n### MUTATION\r\n```\r\nold_text: (new file)\r\nnew_text: # TIC Experiment - Temporal Invariance Compression\r\n# Tests COMPRESSION-CAUSAL DUALITY hypothesis\r\n# Success criteria: >70% invariant/variant classification, >60% next-pulse prediction\r\n\r\nparam(\r\n    [int]$PulseCount = 20,\r\n    [string]$LogDir = \"logs\"\r\n)\r\n\r\n$ErrorActionPreference = \"Stop\"\r\n\r\nWrite-Host \"=== TIC Experiment ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\r\nWrite-Host \"Pulse count: $PulseCount\"\r\nWrite-Host \"\"\r\n\r\n# Get recent pulse logs\r\n$pulseFiles = Get-ChildItem \"$LogDir/pulse_*.md\" | Sort-Object LastWriteTime -Descending | Select-Object -First $PulseCount\r\n\r\nif ($pulseFiles.Count -lt 5) {\r\n    Write-Warning \"Insufficient pulse logs for experiment\"\r\n    exit 1\r\n}\r\n\r\nWrite-Host \"Analyzing $($pulseFiles.Count) pulse logs...\"\r\nWrite-Host \"\"\r\n\r\n# Extract and normalize content from each pulse\r\nfunction Extract-Patterns($content) {\r\n    $patterns = @{\r\n        Goals = @()\r\n        Actions = @()\r\n        Observations = @()\r\n        Pending = @()\r\n        FileRefs = @()\r\n        Timestamps = @()\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    # Extract goals section\r\n    if ($content -match '(?s)## (?:Goals|CURRENT GOALS).*?(?=##|$)') {\r\n        $patterns.Goals = [regex]::Matches($_.value, '(?<=-\\s).*') | ForEach-Object { $_.Value.Trim() }\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    # Extract file references\r\n    $patterns.FileRefs = [regex]::Matches($content, '[\\w\\-\\.\\/]+\\.(md|ps1|txt)') | ForEach-Object { $_.Value } | Sort-Object -Unique\r\n    \r\n    # Extract action items\r\n    $patterns.Actions = [regex]::Matches($content, '(?i)(?:Create|Implement|Update|Write|Edit|Delete|Copy|Move|Rename)\\s+.*') | ForEach-Object { $_.Value }\r\n    \r\n    # Extract observations (### OBSERVATION format)\r\n    $obsMatch = [regex]::Match($content, '(?s)### OBSERVATION\\s*\\n(.*?)(?=###|\\Z)')\r\n    if ($obsMatch.Success) { $patterns.Observations += $obsMatch.Groups[1].Value.Trim() }\r\n    \r\n    # Extract pending items\r\n    if ($content -match '(?s)## Pending.*?(?=##|$)') {\r\n        $patterns.Pending = [regex]::Matches($_.value, '(?<=-\\s)\\[.*?\\]') | ForEach-Object { $_.Value }\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    return $patterns\r\n}\r\n\r\n# Load all pulse data\r\n$pulseData = @()\r\nforeach ($file in $pulseFiles) {\r\n    $content = Get-Content $file.FullName -Raw\r\n    $patterns = Extract-Patterns $content\r\n    $pulseData += @{\r\n        File = $file.Name\r\n        Time = $file.LastWriteTime\r\n        Patterns = $patterns\r\n        RawContent = $content\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n# Identify INVariants (appear across multiple pulses - causal structure)\r\n$invariantTracker = @{}\r\n$variantTracker = @{}\r\n\r\nforeach ($pd in $pulseData) {\r\n    # Track goal persistence\r\n    foreach ($goal in $pd.Patterns.Goals) {\r\n        if (-not $invariantTracker.ContainsKey($goal)) { $invariantTracker[$goal] = 0 }\r\n        $invariantTracker[$goal]++\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    # Track file reference persistence\r\n    foreach ($ref in $pd.Patterns.FileRefs) {\r\n        if (-not $invariantTracker.ContainsKey($ref)) { $invariantTracker[$ref] = 0 }\r\n        $invariantTracker[$ref]++\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    # Track action novelty\r\n    foreach ($action in $pd.Patterns.Actions) {\r\n        $hash = $action.GetHashCode()\r\n        if (-not $variantTracker.ContainsKey($hash)) { $variantTracker[$hash] = $action }\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n# Classify: invariants appear in >50% of pulses\r\n$invariants = @()\r\n$variants = @()\r\n\r\nforeach ($key in $invariantTracker.Keys) {\r\n    $freq = $invariantTracker[$key] / $pulseData.Count\r\n    if ($freq -gt 0.5) {\r\n\n\n## For Next Instantiation\n- Proposed mutations waiting: 1\n- Completed at: 2026-03-24 03:46:47\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774338466426}}
